{"tid":1610140,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想贏香城online，每個人就要揀好職業","createTime":"2019-10-01T16:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T13:34:48.000Z","uid":457,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3e7e47ede83fe31cc5d1cbf717d0b13a4f3a47e8","tid":1610140,"uid":457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:29:04.000Z","msg":"唔係講緊揀做和理非定勇武，而係更加仔細嘅分工<br />\n發夢喺前線見到啲狗一射TG中後排就會冇跌序咁走，前排就一兼數職，一時滅煙一時投擲，其實好冇效率，所以喺黑警眼中我哋而家就係散沙。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以而家開始麻煩各位根據自己嘅喜好同能力揀定職業︰<br />\n例如大膽嘅就拎盾牌上前保護後面+帶領手足步步向前推進<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n臂力大嘅就做投擲兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、中意範圍攻擊就做魔法師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n靈活好眼力嘅就做滅煙小隊或者哨兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算和理非都有唔同職業俾你揀，有收入嘅做補給兵，唔想企太前咪做運輸兵幫手傳物資囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n熟附近地型嘅就配合哨兵幫手足搵路退場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但有一點要記住，揀好職業就要做好本分，冇心理準備就去中後排，切忌偽勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之一句講晒，咁多位一定要認清自己定位，咁先可以打出個form。舉個例，狗放TG同舉旗嗰陣，大家唔係要散，係要大家謹守崗位，前排嘅知道後排會提供支援同cover，後排嘅相信前排有人極速滅煙先會keep住support，之後先可以1212向前推，真正做到齊上齊落。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後我知大家有時會打到好頹，但希望各位唔好忘記我哋係為咗爭取啲咩先企出嚟，只有堅持落去先可以攞返我哋應得嘅，亦都只有堅持落去先對得住幾位烈士同千幾位受傷/被捕手足。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"dc623f64a5130d50e9120dba3e0f805bf121aa40","tid":1610140,"uid":457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:29:41.000Z","msg":"唔好揀錯職業呀大家"},{"pid":"23651cb99f97d42f1f829f17db5f91b717b5c225","tid":1610140,"uid":68414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:30:35.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"08b3e13d25df652a4b805b8de96751aee5d7c17a","tid":1610140,"uid":457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:30:39.000Z","msg":"打咗好耐 幫手推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb1de151afaccda5fceb47113fda56b1902331b","tid":1610140,"uid":457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:31:33.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0466325d9eb12c1998a9f7211e19f87038bc3b9","tid":1610140,"uid":206869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:31:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c679cd03dd506000da0f2889205cd8525da12bb0","tid":1610140,"uid":4767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:32:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce62c09f12cb049d943ed16421f0b964c410e36","tid":1610140,"uid":457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:33:26.000Z","msg":"推上熱門pls"},{"pid":"c078f8f23aa3731b714f19509c65f798424efaaa","tid":1610140,"uid":60749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:33:50.000Z","msg":"到底點先可以做得返捉實前面背囊退<br />\n而唔係掉轉頭跑<br />\n<br />\n同埋就算你要掉轉頭跑 跑幾步望一望後面啦<br />\n到真係防線完全崩潰先跑online啦<br />\n有時連狗都未見到 就跑到九丈幾遠<br />\n嚇兩嚇就成條防線同backup都無曬<br />\n我係狗搵人放風得啦 使撚同你鬥跑鬥打<br />\n等你跑完一大輪 再慢慢收網 慳水慳力"},{"pid":"00c96079dd003c61cb12adbf2454897ba1309a58","tid":1610140,"uid":98787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:36:15.000Z","msg":"推呀推呀推呀"},{"pid":"77672003f473553f7ccbcb41f18cf81c6e1b4453","tid":1610140,"uid":457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c078f8f23aa3731b714f19509c65f798424efaaa","tid":1610140,"uid":60749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:33:50.000Z","msg":"到底點先可以做得返捉實前面背囊退<br />\n而唔係掉轉頭跑<br />\n<br />\n同埋就算你要掉轉頭跑 跑幾步望一望後面啦<br />\n到真係防線完全崩潰先跑online啦<br />\n有時連狗都未見到 就跑到九丈幾遠<br />\n嚇兩嚇就成條防線同backup都無曬<br />\n我係狗搵人放風得啦 使撚同你鬥跑鬥打<br />\n等你跑完一大輪 再慢慢收網 慳水慳力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:36:22.000Z","msg":"根本狂射tg已經嚇到啲人亂晒<br />\n所以其實好需要專業滅煙小隊專業滅煙<br />\n咁到時大家個心先會定啲"},{"pid":"5963634dabcbaee7a28502bd11f7f75f6aae8c37","tid":1610140,"uid":457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:36:36.000Z","msg":"推上熱門thx"},{"pid":"5b383552b3b24ed4ddc05d47e087bf5ecc6286fa","tid":1610140,"uid":457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:37:25.000Z","msg":"仲未喺熱門見到呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40309defc8e44228bfdf682f265f1c998d05cd9","tid":1610140,"uid":457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:37:59.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ffc1154ab5865b3d8692dd3e0bd9cd595d76c38","tid":1610140,"uid":457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:39:17.000Z","msg":"真係要咁做㗎，麻煩大家睇完個post幫手推下"},{"pid":"9eb9c963483885163d88f479614d04ab5fe1a754","tid":1610140,"uid":315356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:39:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bbfbb17c4b91b9572ce69d31b263f0ca03a8b9c","tid":1610140,"uid":285622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:39:53.000Z","msg":"認同 宜家衰在我地對手足既信任程度未夠 大家仲係好獨立既個體 做既決定只為自己負責 唔係為群體負責 變左後排唔信前線會擋住 前線又驚後排突然消失"},{"pid":"eb682b5c83c89c67e5381eeb6de1e2e8c4b03ab8","tid":1610140,"uid":158313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:40:20.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8332844760af584a5a5235922f9e5ce30e29cc","tid":1610140,"uid":152498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:40:33.000Z","msg":"分工真係好重要 <br />\n每次發夢見到好多人都無目的咁遊盪<br />\n浪費資源 又無效率 諗好自己職業可以解決呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n分好職業都可以避免前線真勇武想衝 突然後排又走晒 俾偽勇武人數呃左 亦俾大家知道究竟當時從事進攻既人夠唔夠 再判斷下一步點做 <br />\n<br />\n而如果真係純和理非 純粹充撐場面既 就企後d 企梳d  同慢慢退 相信其他職業既能力 唔好一有tg就兵荒馬亂<br />\n<br />\n大家謹守崗位 齊上齊做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4bf42fe7ebeaf3776dbbc145ca1854465db374","tid":1610140,"uid":285622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:43:15.000Z","msg":"攞番金鐘做例子 俾人側擊其實要守 如果唔守 正路既前線會俾人包炒 但宜家正前會好擔心俾人側擊 因為中後排一退就中空 變左佢地一聽到包抄 其實都唔知退唔退好 因為一包抄中後排撤哂"},{"pid":"d2213353c303a5d0bcdf0afc11feafad9547caf3","tid":1610140,"uid":457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bbfbb17c4b91b9572ce69d31b263f0ca03a8b9c","tid":1610140,"uid":285622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:39:53.000Z","msg":"認同 宜家衰在我地對手足既信任程度未夠 大家仲係好獨立既個體 做既決定只為自己負責 唔係為群體負責 變左後排唔信前線會擋住 前線又驚後排突然消失"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:45:22.000Z","msg":"今日發夢好幾次都係咁 中後排走得太快 前排得返十幾廿人都唔知點好<br />\n一係就偽勇武企最前但有事上嚟就跑最快 搞到中後排死晒<br />\n如果揀好職業大家互相信任就冇呢啲問題"},{"pid":"d79f5e7909f32af5ab9dbd032ccd77dba2ad21b9","tid":1610140,"uid":152498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bbfbb17c4b91b9572ce69d31b263f0ca03a8b9c","tid":1610140,"uid":285622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:39:53.000Z","msg":"認同 宜家衰在我地對手足既信任程度未夠 大家仲係好獨立既個體 做既決定只為自己負責 唔係為群體負責 變左後排唔信前線會擋住 前線又驚後排突然消失"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:45:24.000Z","msg":"Well said <br />\n所以要揀岩自己職業 自己真係會做個樣野同唔抗拒  亦都會堅守 咁大家個信任會build up 到"},{"pid":"f5b977220abdfdbdaee7c7c5d364d6f43da86393","tid":1610140,"uid":457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c8332844760af584a5a5235922f9e5ce30e29cc","tid":1610140,"uid":152498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:40:33.000Z","msg":"分工真係好重要 <br />\n每次發夢見到好多人都無目的咁遊盪<br />\n浪費資源 又無效率 諗好自己職業可以解決呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n分好職業都可以避免前線真勇武想衝 突然後排又走晒 俾偽勇武人數呃左 亦俾大家知道究竟當時從事進攻既人夠唔夠 再判斷下一步點做 <br />\n<br />\n而如果真係純和理非 純粹充撐場面既 就企後d 企梳d  同慢慢退 相信其他職業既能力 唔好一有tg就兵荒馬亂<br />\n<br />\n大家謹守崗位 齊上齊做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:47:34.000Z","msg":"exactly<br />\n而家啲狗一邊衝一邊射tg就輕易收我哋皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"995e169f060d9cde073db6b08a454b4446ec8e22","tid":1610140,"uid":457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:48:59.000Z","msg":"求下大家搞清楚自己定位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63e23757055d5734ffd177ef1a5688fb436cb660","tid":1610140,"uid":457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:51:38.000Z","msg":"推呀"}]}